data.description: This beautiful 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom home on an oversized, cul de sac lot has been carefully maintained by its original owners in the desirable River Stone swim/tennis subdivision. The home features recent improvements such as an architectural roof, tankless water heater, and exterior paint.  Laundry is a breeze when you have an upstairs laundry room with a sink!  Enjoy easy highway access in addition to the convenience of nearby shops, retailers, restaurants, parks, and golf courses. This enviable neighborhood is zoned for Brookwood High School, which has once again been recognized by U.S. News & World Report as a top-ranking high school and was named an AP Honor School in six categories by the Georgia Dept. of Education.  The great location, excellent schools and established community make this affordable home a great option for your real estate investment!
